{"tid":618887,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"無限惡搞C朗銅像大翻身，雕塑家含淚重塑新銅像","createTime":"2018-04-06T07:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T07:52:12.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7d829fcd77d6642d53bd8f6486cdbc7ecfeb7bdd","tid":618887,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"05/04/2018<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/juicy-daily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/img_2016.jpg?resize=640%2C323\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fjuicy-daily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2Fimg_2016.jpg%3Fresize%3D640%252C323&h=ebcaa1e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/juicy-daily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/img_2020.jpg?resize=640%2C432\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fjuicy-daily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2Fimg_2020.jpg%3Fresize%3D640%252C432&h=5e981f4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得上年俾人無限惡搞嘅世界足球先生基斯坦奴銅像？如果唔記得或者未見過，請參考下圖，自行回帶。冇錯呢舊面容扭曲，左面肌肉呈抽搐狀嘅頭像就係名揚天下嘅世界足球先生C朗，個像放係C朗家鄉馬拉德機場，當時仲搵到C朗親自剪綵揭幕。不過睇嚟當時連c朗都唔太滿意個銅像。<br />\n<br />\n製作銅像嘅雕塑家Emanuel Santos完成銅像製作之後都相當滿意製成品，誰不知最後作品畀人無限惡搞，負皮不絕，媒體一致狂踩，雕塑家Emanuel 回憶呢段經歷嘅時候更一度委屈到落淚，不過正所謂：「那些打不死你的人，將會令你變得更堅強！」雕塑家Emanuel 得到一次復仇機會，喺邊度跌低喺邊度企返起身，佢得到一次重新雕塑C朗銅像的機會。<br />\n<br />\nEmanuel回憶第一個c朗銅像改變了他，令他學會面對其他人嘅批評，佢希望藉雕塑第二個c朗銅像教育個仔，令佢明白「衹要自己做緊一件自己享受嘅事情，唔好俾外間負評打敗，衹要我哋能夠堅持落去，都會成為人生勝利組。」好勵志！<br />\n<br />\n批評人好容易，尤其係接近冇成本嘅批評網上世界，但呢啲批評可能對承受嘅人帶來沉重打擊。Emanuel新造嘅銅像雖然都唔係完美，但對佢自己來講已經算係一個鹹魚翻生。大家覺得新嘅C朗銅像究竟似唔似佢本人？"},{"pid":"86ce17bb543607c2bdf5463a86c6fe54aa8fc179","tid":618887,"uid":50591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"ebb67969a8092e9c17f8d6b954fa82b364f3ad26","tid":618887,"uid":90515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/153650_8f118be75dd0374fdb366c92a3526bec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F153650_8f118be75dd0374fdb366c92a3526bec.png&h=88f914b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實都幾過份，就算話係跟住阿朗整容前黎整都完全唔似"},{"pid":"7851582e06c6c25df3fd305c401e4771e8ae4e75","tid":618887,"uid":166126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:43:09.000Z","msg":"美斯連重新整銅像都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/a8/51/lionel-messi-barcelona-vandalism_8i8og04o5gx1mr06x5xlmk9i.jpg?t=550840160&amp;quality=100&amp;w=640&amp;h=360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2Fa8%2F51%2Flionel-messi-barcelona-vandalism_8i8og04o5gx1mr06x5xlmk9i.jpg%3Ft%3D550840160%26quality%3D100%26w%3D640%26h%3D360&h=2ad3c90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/www.goal.com/zh-hk/amp/新聞/美斯-銅像-再次-被毀/1e38yu8vdh8tk1k2wvceckpjn9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fwww.goal.com%2Fzh-hk%2Famp%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF-%E9%8A%85%E5%83%8F-%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1-%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%80%2F1e38yu8vdh8tk1k2wvceckpjn9&d=UhcK7O4HZ2YeQOuwrYoL8hFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=e2a681b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/www.goal.com/zh-hk/amp/新聞/美斯-銅像-再次-被毀/1e38yu8vdh8tk1k2wvceckpjn9</a><br />\n球王都有對頭人！位於阿根廷布宜諾斯艾利斯的美斯銅像，繼今年1月後再次被毀，整個倒在地上，但暫時未知「兇手」誰屬。"},{"pid":"77987b3bd34fc27479c86f1a431786a0107abdce","tid":618887,"uid":90515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7851582e06c6c25df3fd305c401e4771e8ae4e75","tid":618887,"uid":166126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:43:09.000Z","msg":"美斯連重新整銅像都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/a8/51/lionel-messi-barcelona-vandalism_8i8og04o5gx1mr06x5xlmk9